These are templates used in my user namespace, but won't likely be useful anywhere else. Some templates that create direct edit links to pages in my user space, or templates which contain my signature, have been protected against transclusion into other pages besides my user space. Other templates may be used in other places, if needed. I will revert any changes made to these templates: if changes need to be made to suit them for a particular application, please copy the code to a new location and edit it there.

