Swedish School starts when children are seven years old to fifteen years old. If they want to they can choose to go to high school, if they do it they g there from that they are sixteen years old to that they are nineteen years old.
In this time they learn: * svenska = Swedish * historia = history * idrott = PE * matematik (formal), matte (casual) = mathematics (maths) * NO, Natur Orientering = Physics and other nature sciences (lit. nature orientation) * SO, Social Orientering = social knowledge (lit.Social Orientation) * engelska = English * B-språk = free choice of a third language to learn, optional * C-språk = free choice of a fourth language to learn, optional
